<h3>Seasonal Content Planning</h3>
<p>Local businesses are seasonal. Plan content around what drives your business.</p>
<p><strong>Restaurants:</strong> Seasonal menu launches, holiday specials, event nights, food festival participation.</p>
<p><strong>Home services:</strong> Spring cleaning, summer maintenance, fall prep, winter emergency readiness.</p>
<p><strong>Retail:</strong> Back-to-school, holiday gift guides, seasonal collections, local market appearances.</p>
<p><strong>Professional services:</strong> Tax season reminders, end-of-year planning, New Year goal-setting content.</p>
<p>Build a 12-month content skeleton at the start of each year. Fill in specific posts monthly. This approach prevents the "content blank" that leads to posting silence.</p>
<h3>Using Scheduling Tools</h3>
